#Calculation of early precision
#Count the total edges in the true network
tot_edge_GT<-sum(!!true_net) 
tot_edge_EST<-vector()
EP<-vector()
EBICgraph_binary<-list(matrix(data=NA,nrow=ncol(data[[1]]),ncol=ncol(data[[1]])))
for(i in 1:length(data))
{
  tot_edge_EST[i]<-sum(!!EBICgraph[[i]])
  if(tot_edge_EST[i]<tot_edge_GT)
  {
    EBICgraph_binary[[i]]<-binarize(abs(kmat(EBICgraph[[i]],
                                             tot_edge_EST[i])),threshold = 0.1)
    
    EP[i]<-sum(!!EBICgraph_binary[[i]])/tot_edge_EST[i]
  }
  else
    EBICgraph_binary[[i]]<-binarize(abs(kmat(EBICgraph[[i]],
                                             tot_edge_GT)),threshold = 0.1)
    EP[i]<-sum(!!EBICgraph_binary[[i]])/tot_edge_GT
}
mean(EP)
sd(EP)
